accTitle: Mermaid create and destroy
accDescr {
Demonstrates Mermaid actor lifecycle control, including destroy-before-create and recreate.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/17-create-destroy/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/17-create-destroy
}
